117
00:06:11,089 --> 00:06:12,189
I guess not.

118
00:06:13,392 --> 00:06:14,742
Hang on a second.

119
00:06:16,883 --> 00:06:18,965
Let's not throw that idea out
so quickly.

120
00:06:19,354 --> 00:06:22,110
- What do you mean?
- Well, realistically,

121
00:06:22,235 --> 00:06:25,640
