to buy Lyndsey a birthday present.

144
00:07:23,311 --> 00:07:24,994
All right, here's what I'm gonna do.

145
00:07:25,119 --> 00:07:27,590
I'm gonna lend you enough
so you can buy her something nice.

146
00:07:28,110 --> 00:07:30,240
- How much?
- Are you kidding?

147
00:07:30,365 --> 00:07:33,067
- You're negotiating with me?
- Forget it.

148
00:07:33,192 --> 00:07:36,015
I appreciate the offer,
but I'm not gonna take your money.

149
00:07:36,321 --> 00:07:39,654
I'm sorry. I think
I might have just had a small stroke.

150
00:07:39,779 --> 00:07:41,604
You're not gonna take my money?

151
00:07:42,032 --> 00:07:43,450
You heard me right.

152
00:07:43,575 --> 00:07:46,258
I have to find a way
to buy Lyndsey a nice present on my own.

153
00:07:46,383 --> 00:07:49,403
- It's a matter of self-respect.
- Little late for that, isn't it?

154
00:07:49,572 --> 00:07:51,359
If it was for me,
I'd take your money.

155
00:07:51,484 --> 00:07:53,324
If it was for you,
I wouldn't offer it.

156
00:07:53,534 --> 00:07:55,104
